{"tid":353870,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"ram入門級問題","createTime":"2017-08-10T03:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T16:08:38.000Z","uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"463fbc54a0dbde4c6c7871984851e6106e445b33","tid":353870,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"一般裝多條ram嘅話，都係4gb配4gb, 8gb配8gb<br />\n咁可唔可以4gb配8gb呢？"},{"pid":"8f3c6c044ba18d7e3d74ae3aa8d68bac633f7cdb","tid":353870,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:39:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed1ded97a80e1b1f2108ae4d39317478d2e7572","tid":353870,"uid":96983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:42:58.000Z","msg":"得呀 但唔係最好既選擇"},{"pid":"aa8aa2ee95a9933573bf9fe7fcef8c94feb15770","tid":353870,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得呀 但唔係最好既選擇</blockquote><br />\n點解呢？兩條總比一條好呀話？"},{"pid":"c8fb114a69266da89ef891cc87c46932797c8bc0","tid":353870,"uid":74846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得呀 但唔係最好既選擇</blockquote><br />\n點解呢？兩條總比一條好呀話？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔同容量做唔到雙通道會變慢"},{"pid":"c623408c22632c36a1d943ceb8d650c84dfab14a","tid":353870,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>得呀 但唔係最好既選擇</blockquote><br />\n點解呢？兩條總比一條好呀話？</blockquote><br />\nsize 越大越好，但最好既選擇係兩條同size既ram行dual channel"},{"pid":"5763b83da6ec7194d378d3dfc970d1d52fe37939","tid":353870,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:06:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>得呀 但唔係最好既選擇</blockquote><br />\n點解呢？兩條總比一條好呀話？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔同容量做唔到雙通道會變慢</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐係話做唔到雙道既話，兩條反而比一條慢？"},{"pid":"42e30494d097ddec8d116b4efa7b0d166a2576ca","tid":353870,"uid":62521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:10:39.000Z","msg":"咁 2 2 4 4 算唔算dual channel？"},{"pid":"f489ba0125ddede0413d0a67a1b2ec905294ffbe","tid":353870,"uid":8029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:11:05.000Z","msg":"你當ram 就好似一部小巴咁<br />\n<br />\ndual channel 就等於兩部小巴一齊上落客<br />\n點都快過遂部逐部上<br />\n<br />\n但如果你換一部做巴士，行唔到dual channel 佢就要分開上，你裝既人係多左，但上落客個速度會慢左"},{"pid":"20c828adc7962460dbd7023b4dbad35097e5a800","tid":353870,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你當ram 就好似一部小巴咁<br />\n<br />\ndual channel 就等於兩部小巴一齊上落客<br />\n點都快過遂部逐部上<br />\n<br />\n但如果你換一部做巴士，行唔到dual channel 佢就要分開上，你裝既人係多左，但上落客個速度會慢左</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明解，姐係兩條唔同gb既ram雖然行唔到dual channel, 唔係最好配置，但點都比一條好？"},{"pid":"1a268a8e125777955a5f18a0d7cdf8987398d8b3","tid":353870,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"用落冇分別"},{"pid":"10673bf385be7a138aa9a05726d9edd5e943ff80","tid":353870,"uid":8029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:19:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你當ram 就好似一部小巴咁<br />\n<br />\ndual channel 就等於兩部小巴一齊上落客<br />\n點都快過遂部逐部上<br />\n<br />\n但如果你換一部做巴士，行唔到dual channel 佢就要分開上，你裝既人係多左，但上落客個速度會慢左</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明解，姐係兩條唔同gb既ram雖然行唔到dual channel, 唔係最好配置，但點都比一條好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你行既application 好大食<br />\n本身唔夠ram 用，換條大既係應該既<br />\n<br />\n但唔係best practice"},{"pid":"06c563a3acff087bf35165771a6ead1b61707baf","tid":353870,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:23:37.000Z","msg":"謝眾ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登有愛"},{"pid":"382fc3186f31d29e7b2be2a983d3b5dd2354d419","tid":353870,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁 2 2 4 4 算唔算dual channel？</blockquote><br />\n2對返2, 4對返4 (slot setting跟老母板) 就行到dual channel"},{"pid":"eec6aea8b3c6412fee5febff4a132ca02b264f3e","tid":353870,"uid":62521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:43:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁 2 2 4 4 算唔算dual channel？</blockquote><br />\n2對返2, 4對返4 (slot setting跟老母板) 就行到dual channel</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭先check咗下<br />\n<br />\n得2 2行緊dual<br />\n<br />\n4 4 各自行緊single <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f576f06a37abd662c76abd7f49beeb9c17cd0b3e","tid":353870,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁 2 2 4 4 算唔算dual channel？</blockquote><br />\n2對返2, 4對返4 (slot setting跟老母板) 就行到dual channel</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭先check咗下<br />\n<br />\n得2 2行緊dual<br />\n<br />\n4 4 各自行緊single <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n13<br />\n24<br />\n咁樣插"},{"pid":"001acbcabcd679a7398af5a8bcb88d9d5a5202ab","tid":353870,"uid":51858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T21:52:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁 2 2 4 4 算唔算dual channel？</blockquote><br />\n2對返2, 4對返4 (slot setting跟老母板) 就行到dual channel</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭先check咗下<br />\n<br />\n得2 2行緊dual<br />\n<br />\n4 4 各自行緊single <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n13<br />\n24<br />\n咁樣插</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n22行到dual咁照計佢都係13 24咁插喎"},{"pid":"11cde3bb5c11805fdcda1a8ba20f0c1bdf119ced","tid":353870,"uid":31022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T02:31:00.000Z","msg":"我4 4 4 4咁插 但係開機冇畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1333 1600 1333 1600"},{"pid":"a10844161f0e0fa4b43723bcd467281ad9649af0","tid":353870,"uid":51858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我4 4 4 4咁插 但係開機冇畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1333 1600 1333 1600</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係有野壞，試下一條一條咁插"},{"pid":"ec6760b53c6a18ed36ad36e861e68e628383b338","tid":353870,"uid":31022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T09:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我4 4 4 4咁插 但係開機冇畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1333 1600 1333 1600</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係有野壞，試下一條一條咁插</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係唔相容?"},{"pid":"0cfc2f7cd309c5c7684cbd4b4978ac7f4714e866","tid":353870,"uid":51858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我4 4 4 4咁插 但係開機冇畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1333 1600 1333 1600</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係有野壞，試下一條一條咁插</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係唔相容?</blockquote><br />\n好少話會唔相容<br />\n就算係都係慢d無dual channel<br />\n唔會無畫面<br />\n<br />\n你先落一條ram,試下開唔開到機<br />\n<br />\n開到既話用依條ram試晒4條槽睇下係咪槽既問題<br />\n<br />\n如果唔關條槽事就一條一條咁試埋淨低3條ram,睇下係咪壞ram"},{"pid":"f10f039011a87e2eeeb0ff3e0c2e5f3f75aa5d5e","tid":353870,"uid":31022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我4 4 4 4咁插 但係開機冇畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1333 1600 1333 1600</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係有野壞，試下一條一條咁插</blockquote><br />\n會唔會係唔相容?</blockquote><br />\n好少話會唔相容<br />\n就算係都係慢d無dual channel<br />\n唔會無畫面<br />\n<br />\n你先落一條ram,試下開唔開到機<br />\n<br />\n開到既話用依條ram試晒4條槽睇下係咪槽既問題<br />\n<br />\n如果唔關條槽事就一條一條咁試埋淨低3條ram,睇下係咪壞ram</blockquote><br />\n好 唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc1131cbf069b428bb579b66487d15e7adc3146","tid":353870,"uid":101593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我4 4 4 4咁插 但係開機冇畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n1333 1600 1333 1600</blockquote><br />\n唔同頻率既話 最低頻率既要放第一個slot 好似係<br />\n試下1600 1333 1600 1333"},{"pid":"a5b9ddb9c63432c76194ba774c10a1880a6a2062","tid":353870,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:24:53.000Z","msg":"我部notebook兩條DDR4 ram，由於一條係買機時佢送俾我後加既，所以唔同牌子，我係Speccy check過佢地Max Bandwidth，一條寫「DDR4-2134 (1067 MHz)」，另一條就寫「DDR4-2132 (1066MHz)」，兩者相差1MHz，會唔會因此行唔到Dual Channel架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我點知佢係咪行緊Dual Channel？"},{"pid":"e66864644a9e09efdb134ac97ae54f1bc4894a0a","tid":353870,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:51:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我部notebook兩條DDR4 ram，由於一條係買機時佢送俾我後加既，所以唔同牌子，我係Speccy check過佢地Max Bandwidth，一條寫「DDR4-2134 (1067 MHz)」，另一條就寫「DDR4-2132 (1066MHz)」，兩者相差1MHz，會唔會因此行唔到Dual Channel架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我點知佢係咪行緊Dual Channel？</blockquote><br />\nDL個CPU-Z睇下就知"}]}